    - **Languages**: Python, C++, JavaScript (Beginner)
    - **Tools**: Git, VSCode, Jupyter Notebook
    - **Other Interests**: Machine Learning, Artificial Intelligence, Web Development
""")

# Section 4: Achievements (as a student)
st.header("Achievements")
